new.description: The FreeRDP - Out-of-Bounds Read (CVE-2024-32459) vulnerability concerns FreeRDP, a free implementation of Remote Desktop Protocol. FreeRDP-based clients and servers using a version of FreeRDP prior to version 3.5.0 or 2.11.6 are vulnerable to out-of-bounds reading12. Versions 3.5.0 and 2.11.6 correct the problem
